OL,3,CLord Hague vows to champion 'free
OL,4,Cspeech' as he becomes university's
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FLord Hague told hundreds of attendees
OL,8,Fat the Sheldonian Theatre in Oxford
OL,9,Fthat encouraging "free thought and
OL,10,Fspeech without hatred" was a possible
OL,11,Ftest for institutions.
OL,13,FThe Chancellor welcomed the Labour
OL,14,FGovernment's decision to revive a
OL,15,Fnumber of provisions of the Higher
OL,16,FEducation (Freedom of Speech) Act.
