OL,4,Cspeech' as he becomes university's
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FThe Chancellor is the titular head of
OL,8,Fthe University of Oxford and presides
OL,9,Fover several key ceremonies.
OL,11,FAlong with formal duties, it will be
OL,12,FLord Hague's job as Chancellor to act
OL,13,Fas an ambassador for the University at
OL,14,Fa range of local, national and
OL,15,Finternational events. He will also
OL,16,Fchair the committee for the selection
OL,17,Fof the Vice Chancellor.
