OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FLord Hague was the leader of the
OL,8,FConservative Party from 1997 to 2001,
OL,9,Fand also served as the Shadow Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary between 2005-2010.
OL,12,FHe was educated at Wath-on-Dearne
OL,13,FComprehensive School and Magdalen
OL,14,FCollege, Oxford where he studied
OL,15,Fphilosophy, politics and economics and
OL,16,Fwas President of the Oxford Union.
