OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FIn his speech, Lord Hague also said:
OL,8,F"I thank all of you, the Convocation,
OL,9,Ffor electing me as your chancellor and
OL,10,Ffor your enthusiastic welcome in
OL,11,Frecent weeks.
OL,13,F"Every visit I have made so far and
OL,14,Fevery conversation, has intensified my
OL,15,Fexcitement about the years to come. I
OL,16,Fhappily dedicate myself today to
OL,17,Fworking with you and for you."
