OL,3,CLord Hague vows to champion 'free
OL,4,Cspeech' as he becomes university's
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,F"His deep connection to the University
OL,8,Fand his commitment to its values,
OL,9,Fmission and vision will serve this
OL,10,Fworld-class institution well during
OL,11,Fhis tenure. He is a man of
OL,12,Fconsiderable integrity, wisdom and
OL,13,Fdedication. I look forward to working
OL,14,Fclosely with him in the years ahead as
OL,15,Fwe uphold and strengthen Oxford's
OL,16,Flegacy of excellence."
OL,18,FLord Hague will serve as the new
OL,19,FChancellor for a term of 10 years.
